        Transfer Duty in Queensland: What Sellers Should Know About What Buyers Are Paying
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Transfer duty is the buyer's cost, but it directly shapes their budget, their borrowing capacity, and how hard they negotiate. Understanding it makes you a sharper seller.
      </p>
